<promed@promedmail.org>
[_Schistosoma haematobium_ is known in the Limpopo river system. Outbreaks
may occur if control programmes fail to treat infected people. Information
on the previous prevalence of schistosomiasis in South Africa would be
appreciated. - Mod.EP]
